t-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，如图4所示，论文以双寡头Stackelberg博弈为例，展示框架如何通过标准化提示词把玩家、行动、收益与规则转化为机器可处理的格式，并生成均衡表达式、求解步骤与对应Python代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"192\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"141\" data-imgfileid=\"505187481\" data-ratio=\"0.3417412530512612\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1229\" data-width=\"415\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54bd7374&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1nlR22BibVa7EJXJW8COLcqIJgRibth77gVKT1rOEbCv5IyzTibmRDFEJ4YaO2iaa8iamG5UdgNeYjNKQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图4 双寡头Stackelberg博弈求解架构</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0356db0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">碳市场动态博弈</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PrimeNash的真正威力在于解决现实世界的复杂难题。论文以碳排放权交易市场为例，展示了其在复杂动态博弈中的应用潜力。研究构建了一个包含四个季度交易期的动态博弈模型，利用逆向归纳法（Backward Induction） 求解。在此案例中，PrimeNash产出了该领域首个被严格证明的碳市场闭式解析解。如图5所示，模型不仅推导出了公式，更复现了真实的某些市场现象：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">期末价格波动： 模拟显示，碳价在第1-3期维持低位（约18.65 CNY/t），却在第4期履约截止前急剧飙升至74.71 CNY/t。这种「翘尾效应」与现实市场中企业的履约焦虑高度一致。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大型国企的市场影响力： 分析揭示了大型国有企业如何利用其市场地位调节供需，从而影响价格走势。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">政策杠杆R-value： 论文深入探讨了政策参数 R-value（跨期持有激励）的作用。当 R-value 较高时，企业倾向于囤积配额以期未来升值，导致当期供给收缩、价格上涨；反之则会释放流动性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以上量化洞见为政策制定者提供了有力的工具，通过调整参数或监管临近截止期的交易，可以有效平抑市场投机，维持价格稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"244\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"180\" data-imgfileid=\"505187482\" data-ratio=\"0.43498817966903075\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1269\" data-width=\"415\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ad61938&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1nlR22BibVa7EJXJW8COLcqFB55mewBEnhT2np1Bn9pImBmlgSWXROZ8G3lIBN3yTa9sA0QWsqYOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图5 碳市场博弈问题的动态均衡特征</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">论文总结</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PrimeNash作为首个基于LLM智能体的纳什均衡解析求解框架，成功建立了「策略生成—收益评估—均衡证明」的模块化闭环，将闭式Nash均衡推导从依赖专家的手工工作转化为可复现、可审计的计算流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该框架通过多智能体推理、符号代码执行与形式化验证，能够有效处理高维策略、跨期递归以及不连续、非凸收益等难题。在七类经典模型的测试中，PrimeNash实现了对静态博弈的全面求解与对动态博弈的高比例成功求解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">特别是在碳市场竞价博弈案例中，PrimeNash不仅给出了可证明的闭式均衡解，还能复现履约期末波动等关键现象，并将R value等机制参数与市场稳定性建立了可解释的联系，为市场设计与气候政策分析提供了一种透明、可检验的量化工具，标志着AI驱动的科学发现在博弈论与经济学领域迈出了重要一步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">研究团队介绍</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">论文第一作者为南洋理工大学柳文轩博士，香港中文大学（深圳）赵俊华教授为本文的通讯作者，南洋理工大学周茜缘、悉尼大学王馨蕾和香港中文大学（深圳）程裕恒是本文共同第一作者，香港中文大学（深圳）黄建伟教授是本文共同通讯作者。本文其它合作者包括香港中文大学（深圳）叶立新教授、美国西北大学Randall Berry教授及耶鲁大学Leandros Tassiulas教授。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">赵俊华教授领衔的人工智能-能源-经济交叉学科创新团队致力于解决大模型智能体算法、能源系统、电力市场、碳市场领域的前沿基础性科学问题和关键技术，旨在通过学科交叉实现从主体到系统层面的整体解决方案，推动相关领域取得突破性进展。近年来在Joule、Nature Communications、Scientific Data、Nexus等国际期刊上发表系列多学科交叉论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">doi:10.1016/j.ynexs.2025.100107</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span leaf=\"\">秒追ASI</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">⭐点赞、转发、在看一键三连⭐</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 15px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">点亮星标，锁定新智元极速推送！</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"122\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505133683\" data-ratio=\"0.2111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f15ce8a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1y6B5OM79TFzpkceWtUkI6LEwv0uYicSoM5Q3I3kDNJhxWdL3tQvbOpU3Ty7icBqnDDNd4CCu4ibiaHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6129629629629629\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"354\" data-imgfileid=\"505175929\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=99926e57&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCmEg58Ql8HbceG3TGfsewb8Xv49w3kzttrWd4WJiboVLRribHLK1PEZAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2055555555555557\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"1275\" data-imgfileid=\"505177067\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43e4b83d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtkZ7jV1lzPtlWl7VHXia5cBBwXUVfsicjhtsIPWib5qds3GpH9wjKOYMwg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"%27%27\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=5a4d4bb8&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI3MTA0MTk1MA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2652673881%26idx%3D3%26sn%3Db62f0d4af2b7ab70581dbe0ec8fc8d88\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "香港中文大学（深圳）等团队开发了 PrimeNash 框架，利用大语言模型智能体实现了纳什均衡闭式解析解的自动推导与形式化验证。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "香港中文大学（深圳）等团队开发了 PrimeNash 框架，利用大语言模型智能体实现了纳什均衡闭式解析解的自动推导与形式化验证。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了由香港中文大学（深圳）赵俊华、黄建伟教授团队联合多所顶尖高校研发的 PrimeNash 智能体框架。该框架旨在解决复杂博弈中纳什均衡求解的计算挑战，通过策略生成（SGM）、策略评估（SEM）和均衡证明（EPM）三个核心模块，模拟人类数学家的科研路径。PrimeNash 不仅能处理高维、非凸的静态博弈，在动态博弈中也表现出色，成功率达 70%。研究通过碳排放权交易市场的案例，展示了该框架在提供可证明的闭式解析解及解释市场现象（如“翘尾效应”）方面的强大能力，标志着 AI 在博弈论自动化研究领域迈出了重要一步。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "PrimeNash 框架构建了模块化闭环，将博弈论推导从专家手工模式转变为自动化计算流程。",
      "explanation": "该框架包含策略生成、评估与证明三个核心模块，通过模拟数学家的逻辑推理，利用 LLM 的代码生成与符号推导能力，实现了对纳什均衡闭式解析解的自动求解与验证。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入均衡证明模块（EPM），利用严格的数学工具确保了求解结果的严谨性与可解释性。",
      "explanation": "EPM 不依赖模糊估算，而是执行符号推导并应用 KKT 条件或最佳响应定理。这种形式化验证机制不仅能确保结果正确，还能在证明失败时提供精准反馈，驱动系统迭代。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在碳交易市场复杂动态博弈中的应用，展示了该框架解决现实世界大规模经济问题的能力。",
      "explanation": "PrimeNash 产出了碳市场首个被严格证明的闭式解析解，并成功复现了现实中的“翘尾效应”等市场现象，为政策制定者提供了透明、可检验的量化分析工具。"
    }
  ],
